<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.7">
<l>aṟinta ṟintu tēṟit tēṟi yāṉeṉa tāviyuḷḷē</l>
<l>niṟainta ñāṉa mūrtti yāyai niṉmala mākavaittu</l>
<l>piṟantuñ cettu niṉṟiṭaṟum pētaimai tīrnto ḻintēṉ</l>
<l>naṟuntu ḻāyiṉ kaṇṇi yammā nāṉuṉṉaik kaṇṭukoṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Knowing [and] knowing, believing [and] believing, putting inside my soul</l>
<l>the you in the full form of knowledge so as to be spotless,</l>
<l>I have put an end to the folly in which I stumbled, being born and dying,</l>
<l>o father with a fragrant tulsi chaplet, seeing you for myself.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
